items.title: OTT @ WPG
items.description: Extended highlights of the Ottawa Senators at the Winnipeg Jets

items.title: Recap: OTT 2, WPG 1
items.blurb: Chiasson scores go-ahead goal in 3rd to lift Senators
items.description: Alex Chiasson put the Senators on top midway through the 3rd period and Zack Smith also scored in Ottawa's 2-1 win over the Jets

items.title: WSH @ PHI
items.description: Extended highlights of the Washington Capitals at the Philadelphia Flyers

items.title: WSH 1, PHI 2 - F/SO
items.description: Steve Mason made 29 saves in a 2-1 shootout win, giving the Flyers a two-point lead over the Red Wings for the second wild card spot

items.title: CGY @ ANA
items.description: Extended highlights of the Calgary Flames at the Anaheim Ducks

items.title: Recap: CGY 3, ANA 8
items.blurb: Ducks get off to a quick start in win over Flames
items.description: Jakob Silfverberg scored two of the Ducks' eight goals as they got off to a fast start in their 8-3 win over the Flames
